locality: E Ankaramy-be, Réserve Spéciale de Manongarivo, Antsatrotro.
Parc National de Ranomafana, Vatoharanana, 40 km SO Ranomafana (Ville). Forêt dense humide de moyenne altitude. Echantillon préservé en alcool.
East of Ankaramy, Reserve Speciale Manongarivo, Antsatrotro, off summit trail on western face, beside a small stream. Montane moss forest. Plants preserved in alcohol.

Reserve Naturelle Integrale d'Andringitra. 50 km S of Ambalavao. Near abandoned meteorological station above Ambalamarina. High altitude moss/lichen rainforest-ericaceous bush. Phillippia dominant above 1975 m. Canopy 5-25 m tall. Grassy/rocky summit with orchids.
Diana, Ambilobe, Manambato, Antsahavalany. Forêt dense sub-humide de moyenne altitude située à 10 Km à vol d'oiseau d'Antsahavalany. Echantillons traités en alcool.

Tsaratanana massif, N of Mangindrano. Along trail from camp at Be Pia to Andranomadio. Montane forest (with lichens). Collected with P. Antilahimena, E. Mick, R. Razakamalala & P. Rahagalala. (Specimens preserved in alcohol).
Diego-Suarez / Antsiranana - Massif de Manongarivo: Bassin de Maitsamalaza, nord-est d'Antsatrotro/Faritanin Antsiranana
